{"chapter_number":72,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":40,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"الجن","name_complex":"Al-Jinn","name_simple":"Al-Jinn","verses_count":28,"pages":[572,573],"meaning":{"text":"The Jinn","en":"The Jinn","id":"Jin"},"verses":[[[1,5448,"72:1","قُلْ أُوحِيَ إِلَيَّ أَنَّهُ اسْتَمَعَ نَفَرٌ مِّنَ الْجِنِّ فَقَالُوا إِنَّا سَمِعْنَا قُرْآنًا عَجَبًا",["Say: It has been revealed to me that a party of the jinn listened, and they said: Surely we have heard a wonderful Quran,","Katakanlah (Muhammad), “Telah diwahyukan kepadaku bahwa sekumpulan jin telah mendengarkan (bacaan),” lalu mereka berkata, “Kami telah mendengarkan bacaan yang menakjubkan (Al-Qur'an),"],572,29,58,229,null,null],[2,5449,"72:2","يَهْدِي إِلَى الرُّشْدِ فَآمَنَّا بِهِ ۖ وَلَن نُّشْرِكَ بِرَبِّنَا أَحَدًا",["Guiding to the right way, so we believe in it, and we will not set up any one with our Lord:","(yang) memberi petunjuk kepada jalan yang benar, lalu kami beriman kepadanya. Dan kami sekali-kali tidak akan mempersekutukan sesuatu pun dengan Tuhan kami,"],572,29,58,229,null,null],[3,5450,"72:3","وَأَنَّهُ تَعَالَىٰ جَدُّ رَبِّنَا مَا اتَّخَذَ صَاحِبَةً وَلَا وَلَدًا",["And that He-- exalted be the majesty of our Lord-- has not taken a consort, nor a son:","dan sesungguhnya Mahatinggi keagungan Tuhan kami, Dia tidak beristri dan tidak beranak.”"],572,29,58,229,null,null],[4,5451,"72:4","وَأَنَّهُ كَانَ يَقُولُ سَفِيهُنَا عَلَى اللَّهِ شَطَطًا",["And that the foolish amongst us used to forge extravagant things against Allah:","Dan sesungguhnya orang yang bodoh di antara kami dahulu selalu mengucapkan (perkataan) yang melampaui batas terhadap Allah,"],572,29,58,229,null,null],[5,5452,"72:5","وَأَنَّا ظَنَنَّا أَن لَّن تَقُولَ الْإِنسُ وَالْجِنُّ عَلَى اللَّهِ كَذِبًا",["And that we thought that men and jinn did not utter a lie against Allah:","dan sesungguhnya kami mengira, bahwa manusia dan jin itu tidak akan mengatakan perkataan yang dusta terhadap Allah,"],572,29,58,229,null,null],[6,5453,"72:6","وَأَنَّهُ كَانَ رِجَالٌ مِّنَ الْإِنسِ يَعُوذُونَ بِرِجَالٍ مِّنَ الْجِنِّ فَزَادُوهُمْ رَهَقًا",["And that persons from among men used to seek refuge with persons from among jinn, so they increased them in wrongdoing:","dan sesungguhnya ada beberapa orang laki-laki dari kalangan manusia yang meminta perlindungan kepada beberapa laki-laki dari jin, tetapi mereka (jin) menjadikan mereka (manusia) bertambah sesat."],572,29,58,229,null,null],[7,5454,"72:7","وَأَنَّهُمْ ظَنُّوا كَمَا ظَنَنتُمْ أَن لَّن يَبْعَثَ اللَّهُ أَحَدًا",["And that they thought as you think, that Allah would not raise anyone:","Dan sesungguhnya mereka (jin) mengira seperti kamu (orang musyrik Mekah) yang juga mengira bahwa Allah tidak akan membangkitkan kembali siapa pun (pada hari Kiamat)."],572,29,58,229,null,null],[8,5455,"72:8","وَأَنَّا لَمَسْنَا السَّمَاءَ فَوَجَدْنَاهَا مُلِئَتْ حَرَسًا شَدِيدًا وَشُهُبًا",["And that we sought to reach heaven, but we found it filled with strong guards and flaming stars.","Dan sesungguhnya kami (jin) telah mencoba mengetahui (rahasia) langit, maka kami mendapatinya penuh dengan penjagaan yang kuat dan panah-panah api,"],572,29,58,229,null,null],[9,5456,"72:9","وَأَنَّا كُنَّا نَقْعُدُ مِنْهَا مَقَاعِدَ لِلسَّمْعِ ۖ فَمَن يَسْتَمِعِ الْآنَ يَجِدْ لَهُ شِهَابًا رَّصَدًا",["And that we used to sit in some of the sitting-places thereof to steal a hearing, but he who would (try to) listen now would find a flame lying in wait for him:","dan sesungguhnya kami (jin) dahulu dapat menduduki beberapa tempat di langit itu untuk mencuri dengar (berita-beritanya). Tetapi sekarang siapa (mencoba) mencuri dengar (seperti itu) pasti akan menjumpai panah-panah api yang mengintai (untuk membakarnya)."],572,29,58,229,null,null],[10,5457,"72:10","وَأَنَّا لَا نَدْرِي أَشَرٌّ أُرِيدَ بِمَن فِي الْأَرْضِ أَمْ أَرَادَ بِهِمْ رَبُّهُمْ رَشَدًا",["And that we know not whether evil is meant for those who are on earth or whether their Lord means to bring them good:","Dan sesungguhnya kami (jin) tidak mengetahui (adanya penjagaan itu) apakah keburukan yang dikehendaki orang yang di bumi ataukah Tuhan mereka menghendaki kebaikan baginya."],572,29,58,229,null,null],[11,5458,"72:11","وَأَنَّا مِنَّا الصَّالِحُونَ وَمِنَّا دُونَ ذَٰلِكَ ۖ كُنَّا طَرَائِقَ قِدَدًا",["And that some of us are good and others of us are below that: we are sects following different ways:","Dan sesungguhnya di antara kami (jin) ada yang shalih dan ada (pula) kebalikannya. Kami menempuh jalan yang berbeda-beda."],572,29,58,229,null,null],[12,5459,"72:12","وَأَنَّا ظَنَنَّا أَن لَّن نُّعْجِزَ اللَّهَ فِي الْأَرْضِ وَلَن نُّعْجِزَهُ هَرَبًا",["And that we know that we cannot escape Allah in the earth, nor can we escape Him by flight:","Dan sesungguhnya kami (jin) telah menduga, bahwa kami tidak akan mampu melepaskan diri (dari kekuasaan) Allah di bumi dan tidak (pula) dapat lari melepaskan diri (dari)-Nya."],572,29,58,229,null,null],[13,5460,"72:13","وَأَنَّا لَمَّا سَمِعْنَا الْهُدَىٰ آمَنَّا بِهِ ۖ فَمَن يُؤْمِن بِرَبِّهِ فَلَا يَخَافُ بَخْسًا وَلَا رَهَقًا",["And that when we heard the guidance, we believed in it; so whoever believes in his Lord, he should neither fear loss nor being overtaken (by disgrace):","Dan sesungguhnya ketika kami (jin) mendengar petunjuk (Al-Qur'an), kami beriman kepadanya. Maka barangsiapa beriman kepada Tuhan, maka tidak perlu ia takut rugi atau berdosa."],572,29,58,229,null,null],[14,5461,"72:14","وَأَنَّا مِنَّا الْمُسْلِمُونَ وَمِنَّا الْقَاسِطُونَ ۖ فَمَنْ أَسْلَمَ فَأُولَٰئِكَ تَحَرَّوْا رَشَدًا",["And that some of us are those who submit, and some of us are the deviators; so whoever submits, these aim at the right way:","Dan di antara kami ada yang Islam dan ada yang menyimpang dari kebenaran. Siapa yang Islam, maka mereka itu telah memilih jalan yang lurus."],573,29,58,229,null,null],[15,5462,"72:15","وَأَمَّا الْقَاسِطُونَ فَكَانُوا لِجَهَنَّمَ حَطَبًا",["And as to the deviators, they are fuel of hell:","Dan adapun yang menyimpang dari kebenaran, maka mereka menjadi bahan bakar bagi neraka Jahanam.”"],573,29,58,229,null,null],[16,5463,"72:16","وَأَن لَّوِ اسْتَقَامُوا عَلَى الطَّرِيقَةِ لَأَسْقَيْنَاهُم مَّاءً غَدَقًا",["And that if they should keep to the (right) way, We would certainly give them to drink of abundant water,","Dan sekiranya mereka tetap berjalan lurus di atas jalan itu (agama Islam), niscaya Kami akan mencurahkan kepada mereka air yang cukup."],573,29,58,229,null,null],[17,5464,"72:17","لِّنَفْتِنَهُمْ فِيهِ ۚ وَمَن يُعْرِضْ عَن ذِكْرِ رَبِّهِ يَسْلُكْهُ عَذَابًا صَعَدًا",["So that We might try them with respect to it; and whoever turns aside from the reminder of his Lord, He will make him enter into an afflicting chastisement:","Dengan (cara) itu Kami hendak menguji mereka. Dan barangsiapa berpaling dari peringatan Tuhannya, niscaya akan dimasukkan-Nya ke dalam azab yang sangat berat."],573,29,58,229,null,null],[18,5465,"72:18","وَأَنَّ الْمَسَاجِدَ لِلَّهِ فَلَا تَدْعُوا مَعَ اللَّهِ أَحَدًا",["And that the mosques are Allah's, therefore call not upon any one with Allah:","Dan sesungguhnya masjid-masjid itu adalah untuk Allah. Maka janganlah kamu menyembah apa pun di dalamnya selain Allah."],573,29,58,229,null,null],[19,5466,"72:19","وَأَنَّهُ لَمَّا قَامَ عَبْدُ اللَّهِ يَدْعُوهُ كَادُوا يَكُونُونَ عَلَيْهِ لِبَدًا",["And that when the servant of Allah stood up calling upon Him, they wellnigh crowded him (to death).","Dan sesungguhnya ketika hamba Allah (Muhammad) berdiri menyembah-Nya (melaksanakan shalat), mereka (jin-jin) itu berdesakan mengerumuninya."],573,29,58,229,null,null],[20,5467,"72:20","قُلْ إِنَّمَا أَدْعُو رَبِّي وَلَا أُشْرِكُ بِهِ أَحَدًا",["Say: I only call upon my Lord, and I do not associate any one with Him.","Katakanlah (Muhammad), “Sesungguhnya aku hanya menyembah Tuhanku dan aku tidak mempersekutukan sesuatu pun dengan-Nya.”"],573,29,58,229,null,null],[21,5468,"72:21","قُلْ إِنِّي لَا أَمْلِكُ لَكُمْ ضَرًّا وَلَا رَشَدًا",["Say: I do not control for you evil or good.","Katakanlah (Muhammad), “Aku tidak kuasa menolak mudarat maupun mendatangkan kebaikan kepadamu.”"],573,29,58,229,null,null],[22,5469,"72:22","قُلْ إِنِّي لَن يُجِيرَنِي مِنَ اللَّهِ أَحَدٌ وَلَنْ أَجِدَ مِن دُونِهِ مُلْتَحَدًا",["Say: Surely no one can protect me against Allah, nor can I find besides Him any place of refuge:","Katakanlah (Muhammad), “Sesungguhnya tidak ada sesuatu pun yang dapat melindungiku dari (azab) Allah dan aku tidak akan memperoleh tempat berlindung selain dari-Nya."],573,29,58,229,null,null],[23,5470,"72:23","إِلَّا بَلَاغًا مِّنَ اللَّهِ وَرِسَالَاتِهِ ۚ وَمَن يَعْصِ اللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُ فَإِنَّ لَهُ نَارَ جَهَنَّمَ خَالِدِينَ فِيهَا أَبَدًا",["(It is) only a delivering (of communications) from Allah and His messages; and whoever disobeys Allah and His Messenger surely he shall have the fire of hell to abide therein for a long time.","(Aku hanya) menyampaikan (peringatan) dari Allah dan risalah-Nya. Dan barangsiapa mendurhakai Allah dan Rasul-Nya maka sesungguhnya dia akan mendapat (azab) neraka Jahanam, mereka kekal di dalamnya selama-lamanya.”"],573,29,58,229,null,null],[24,5471,"72:24","حَتَّىٰ إِذَا رَأَوْا مَا يُوعَدُونَ فَسَيَعْلَمُونَ مَنْ أَضْعَفُ نَاصِرًا وَأَقَلُّ عَدَدًا",["Until when they see what they are threatened with, then shall they know who is weaker in helpers and fewer in number.","Sehingga apabila mereka melihat (azab) yang diancamkan kepadanya, maka mereka akan mengetahui siapakah yang lebih lemah penolongnya dan lebih sedikit jumlahnya."],573,29,58,229,null,null],[25,5472,"72:25","قُلْ إِنْ أَدْرِي أَقَرِيبٌ مَّا تُوعَدُونَ أَمْ يَجْعَلُ لَهُ رَبِّي أَمَدًا",["Say: I do not know whether that with which you are threatened be nigh or whether my Lord will appoint for it a term:","Katakanlah (Muhammad), “Aku tidak mengetahui, apakah azab yang diancamkan kepadamu itu sudah dekat ataukah Tuhanku menetapkan waktunya masih lama.”"],573,29,58,229,null,null],[26,5473,"72:26","عَالِمُ الْغَيْبِ فَلَا يُظْهِرُ عَلَىٰ غَيْبِهِ أَحَدًا",["The Knower of the unseen! so He does not reveal His secrets to any,","Dia Mengetahui yang gaib, tetapi Dia tidak memperlihatkan kepada siapa pun tentang yang gaib itu."],573,29,58,229,null,null],[27,5474,"72:27","إِلَّا مَنِ ارْتَضَىٰ مِن رَّسُولٍ فَإِنَّهُ يَسْلُكُ مِن بَيْنِ يَدَيْهِ وَمِنْ خَلْفِهِ رَصَدًا",["Except to him whom He chooses as a messenger; for surely He makes a guard to march before him and after him,","Kecuali kepada rasul yang diridhai-Nya, maka sesungguhnya Dia mengadakan penjaga-penjaga (malaikat) di depan dan di belakangnya."],573,29,58,229,null,null],[28,5475,"72:28","لِّيَعْلَمَ أَن قَدْ أَبْلَغُوا رِسَالَاتِ رَبِّهِمْ وَأَحَاطَ بِمَا لَدَيْهِمْ وَأَحْصَىٰ كُلَّ شَيْءٍ عَدَدًا",["So that He may know that they have truly delivered the messages of their Lord, and He encompasses what is with them and He records the number of all things.","Agar Dia mengetahui bahwa rasul-rasul itu sungguh telah menyampaikan risalah Tuhannya, sedang (ilmu-Nya) meliputi apa yang ada pada mereka, dan Dia menghitung segala sesuatu satu persatu."],573,29,58,229,null,null]],[[[1,3,572,"&#xfb51;","word","قُلْ",["Say","mendengarkan"]],[2,3,572,"&#xfb52;","word","أُوحِيَ",["It has been revealed","sekumpulan"]],[3,3,572,"&#xfb53;","word","إِلَيَّ",["to me","dari"]],[4,3,572,"&#xfb54;","word","أَنَّهُ",["that","jin"]],[5,3,572,"&#xfb55;","word","اسْتَمَعَ",["listened","lalu mereka berkata"]],[6,3,572,"&#xfb56;","word","نَفَرٌ",["a group","sesungguhnya kami"]],[7,3,572,"&#xfb57;","word","مِنَ",["of","kami telah mendengar"]],[8,3,572,"&#xfb58;","word","الْجِنِّ",["the jinn","Al Qur'an"]],[9,3,572,"&#xfb59;","word","فَقَالُوا",["and they said","menakjubkan/mengagungkan"]],[10,3,572,"&#xfb5a;","word","إِنَّا",["Indeed, we",""]],[11,3,572,"&#xfb5b;","word","سَمِعْنَا",["heard",""]],[12,3,572,"&#xfb5c;","word","قُرْآنًا",["a Quran",""]],[13,4,572,"&#xfb5d;","word","عَجَبًا",["amazing",""]],[14,4,572,"&#xfb5e;","end","ﭞ",[nu